text: The bottlenose whales are a type of beaked whales that form the genus Hyperoodon. They only have two species, the northern and southern bottlenose whale. == Species == * Hyperoodon ampullatus Forster, 1770 (Northern bottlenose whale) * Hyperoodon planifrons Flower, 1882 (Southern bottlenose whale) == References == Category:Cetaceans Category:Whales
title: Bottlenose whale
